title: Bellydance-O-Rama Vol 1 DVD Performances By (Aliyah Ammal, Virgi
description:
Bellydance-O-Rama Vol 1

This DVD is full of some really good performances. I have noticed from watching that Leyla Jouvana does feature quite prominently in them. But I gotta say I love this. (even though I think the company drastically overprices, I love this one). And no odd performances!

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

See some of the most spectacular belly dance performances in the world on a great stage with state-of-the-art lighting, sound, and video production!
